/!  Begin Page Content
section.services
	.container
		.row
			.col-lg-12
				h2.text-center Get Your Business Out of the Comfort Zone
				p.lead.text-center A unique and memorable brand is aligned with the heart of your business. Expand your business outreach beyond the known and create an engaging online ecosystem that elevates your mission and client experience.
		.row
			.col-md-4.my-5
				.card.services-content
					= image_tag "homepage/services-website-design-2.jpg", :class=>"card-img", :alt=>"Website Design"
					.card-body
						h4 Website Design
						p A well-designed website is intuitive, and converts visitors to new customers. Let's bring your authentic vision to life by developing a holistic online presence that reasonates with your audience.
						
			.col-md-4.my-5
				.card.services-content
					= image_tag "homepage/services-landing-pages.jpg", :class=>"card-img", :alt=>"Landing Page Design"
					.card-body
						h4 Sales Landing Page Design
						p Looking to launch a campaign soon? Let me handcraft a strategic landing page for you that not only attracts leads but also focuses on the customer journey.
			.col-md-4.my-5
				.card.services-content
					= image_tag "homepage/services-other-offerings.jpg", :class=>"card-img", :alt=>"Other Offerings"
					.card-body
						h4 Additional Offerings
						p Gain clarity on your brand vision and attract new customers with creative assets tailored to you and your ideal audience.

		br
		.row
			.col-lg-12
				.text-center
					= link_to "Explore My Services", services_path, :class=>"btn btn-secondary mr-3"
